	(text "Set up so that when the connector is reversed,\nthe rows get reversed with rows and columns with columns.\n\nROW2 + COL12 is the matrix location of the Fn key so\nif it is reversed that will work.\n\nPB6/7 signals could have been also reversible, but I couldn't\nfigure out what do put on the remaining signal pair so they're doubled."
